org.eclipse.jface.action.IAction
public class AssociateArtifactAction
extends org.eclipse.jface.action.Action

This class performs the associate in a different direction - it is an option on the alternative and will associate that alternative with whatever code element happens to be selected in the Java Package Explorer. A message is displayed to confirm this, of course. If there is no java element selected, the user is informed and no action is taken.

Author:
jburge
